overview: Joey Wong leads the technology developement and innovation efforts for all aspects of the Propagator’s product research and development activities.Joey brings more than 12 years of experience in large scale systems design and operation,web product development.Prior to found Propagator,he held positions in executive president,product development, product management at Justto Tech, Etang.com ,Netease.com(NASDAQ:NTES),and Yeeha Company. He founded a famous portal for watches and luxuries in Chinese.
